reviewText: Love this movie, it's very funny.  Item arrived super fast.

FIRST OF ALL.... YOU NEED TO SPEAK SPANISH
TO BE ABLE TO UNDERSTAND ALL THE FUNNY
SITUATIONS THAT IT IS HAPPENING IN THIS FAMILY.

MOST OF THE MOVIE IS FUNNY BUT THERE ARE
SOME SEGMENTS WHERE THE MOVIE BECOMES
SERIOUS, AND SAD.

MOST OF JOAQUIN PARDAVE MOVIES ARE FUNNY, AND GOOD.

IF YOU ARE INTO SPANISH COMEDIES?, THEN GET THIS MOVIE.
